Sentencas: In the present study the long-term behaviour of two ferritic steels, Crofer 22 APU and Crofer 22H, in contact with a Ni-mesh during exposure in simulated anode gas, Ar-4%H-2-2%H2O, at 700 and 800 degrees C for exposure times up to 3000 h was investigated.
Titulo: Long-term behaviour of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect materials in contact with Ni-mesh during exposure in simulated anode gas at 700 and 800 °C

Sentencas: Ni diffusion from the Ni-mesh into the steel resulted in the formation of an austenitic zone whereas diffusion of iron and chromium from the steel into the Ni-mesh resulted in the formation of chromia base oxides In the Ni-mesh.
Titulo: Long-term behaviour of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect materials in contact with Ni-mesh during exposure in simulated anode gas at 700 and 800 °C

Sentencas: Depending on the chemical composition of the steel, the temperature and the exposure time, interdiffusion processes between ferritic steel and Ni-mesh also resulted in sigma-phase formation at the austenite-ferrite interface and in Laves-phase dissolution in the austenitic zone.
Titulo: Long-term behaviour of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect materials in contact with Ni-mesh during exposure in simulated anode gas at 700 and 800 °C

Sentencas: The extent and morphology of the sigma-phase formation are discussed on the basis of thermodynamic considerations, including reaction paths in the ternary alloy system Fe-Ni-Cr. (C) 2014
Titulo: Long-term behaviour of solid oxide fuel cell interconnect materials in contact with Ni-mesh during exposure in simulated anode gas at 700 and 800 °C
